title: Game.Party.USA.Wii-MARVEL
description:
Game Party for the Wii is a collection of classic skill games from around the world, from American sports venues to European gathering spots. Using the Wii&#039;s unique control interface, you can play classics such as darts; modern favorite such as table hockey and hoop shoot, or participate in multiplayer trivia ontests. More than a half dozen games are available. 
It&#039;s the ultimate party game.
